text: Oh my, Im excited about this environment ! Great one, Next bit we need to do some sketches . In whatever style your prefer, just need you to start blocking concepts, using the elements you choose.
So it should be simple, and we can make annotation on what goes on what, later we need to decide everything before building and we will need to try to sketch more defined ideas
Don't use any 3d software for now, use pictures, use the web, you can use a painting software but stay relatively simple how you are drawing
This should be quick ( don't spend hours on each version, maximum 1h should be your limit ) and you should try to get at least 5 good tries but are different between each other
